    {
      "id": "PopularPost52286",
      "post_content": "To say that this card does nothing is crazy. 8 Life for only 2CC is nothing to scoff at, and basically neutralizes the first couple of turns worth of damage you may or may not have received.\n  \n   \nIn limited format, this card is amazing. It keeps you alive for an extra turn or two, which can make all the diference when you're up against a Vampire Deck that is hammering you with the likes of the [Vampire Lacerator](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vampire Lacerator) or the [Guul Draz Vampire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Guul Draz Vampire).\n  \n   \nThe card also has a ton of synergy with landfall decks, and its instant speed allows it to take advantage of sacrifice cards like [Terramorphic Expanse](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terramorphic Expanse).\n  \n   \nAs a final bonus, it can obviously be used to save damage leveled at a Planeswalker.\n  \n   \n4/5\n  ",
      "posted_by": "Gaussgoat",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost52286\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">To say that this card does nothing is crazy.  8 Life for only 2CC is nothing to scoff at, and basically neutralizes the first couple of turns worth of damage you may or may not have received.\r<br/> <br/>In limited format, this card is amazing.  It keeps you alive for an extra turn or two, which can make all the diference when you're up against a Vampire Deck that is hammering you with the likes of the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Vampire Lacerator\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vampire Lacerator\">Vampire Lacerator</a> or the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Guul Draz Vampire\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Guul Draz Vampire\">Guul Draz Vampire</a>.\r<br/> <br/>The card also has a ton of synergy with landfall decks, and its instant speed allows it to take advantage of sacrifice cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Terramorphic Expanse\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terramorphic Expanse\">Terramorphic Expanse</a>.\r<br/> <br/>As a final bonus, it can obviously be used to save damage leveled at a Planeswalker.\r<br/> <br/>4/5\r<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '52286'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                               